{
  "video_id": "iNDXvJjSniI",
  "title": "Cesar Harada: A novel idea for cleaning up oil spills",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Morton Bast Reviewer: Thu-Huong Ha"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15768.0,
      "end_time": 16800.0,
      "text": "In the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16800.0,
      "end_time": 18640.0,
      "text": "what is the common point"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18640.0,
      "end_time": 24408.0,
      "text": "between oil, plastic and radioactivity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24408.0,
      "end_time": 29625.0,
      "text": "On the top line, this is the BP oil spill:"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29625.0,
      "end_time": 31648.0,
      "text": "billions of barrels of oil gushing"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31648.0,
      "end_time": 33170.0,
      "text": "in the Gulf of Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33170.0,
      "end_time": 35192.0,
      "text": "The middle line is millions of tons of"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35192.0,
      "end_time": 37596.0,
      "text": "plastic debris accumulating in our ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37596.0,
      "end_time": 40315.0,
      "text": "and the third line is radioactive material"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40316.0,
      "end_time": 42612.0,
      "text": "leaking from Fukushima nuclear power plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42612.0,
      "end_time": 43950.0,
      "text": "in the Pacific Ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43950.0,
      "end_time": 48533.0,
      "text": "Well, the three big problems have in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48533.0,
      "end_time": 51348.0,
      "text": "that they are man-made problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51348.0,
      "end_time": 53404.0,
      "text": "but they are controlled by natural forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53404.0,
      "end_time": 57812.0,
      "text": "This should make us feel very, terribly awful"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57812.0,
      "end_time": 60138.0,
      "text": "as much as it should make us feel hopeful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60139.0,
      "end_time": 62948.0,
      "text": "because if we have the power to create these problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62948.0,
      "end_time": 64628.0,
      "text": "we may as well have the power"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64628.0,
      "end_time": 66600.0,
      "text": "to remediate these problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66600.0,
      "end_time": 68400.0,
      "text": "But what about natural forces?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68400.0,
      "end_time": 70987.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s exactly what I want to talk about today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70987.0,
      "end_time": 73292.0,
      "text": "is how we can use these natural forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73292.0,
      "end_time": 78515.0,
      "text": "to remediate these man-made problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78515.0,
      "end_time": 79741.0,
      "text": "When the BP oil spill happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79741.0,
      "end_time": 82506.0,
      "text": "I was working at MIT, and I was in charge"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82506.0,
      "end_time": 84903.0,
      "text": "of developing an oil spill-cleaning technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84903.0,
      "end_time": 88316.0,
      "text": "And I had a chance to go in the Gulf of Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88316.0,
      "end_time": 90653.0,
      "text": "and meet some fishermen and see"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90653.0,
      "end_time": 92444.0,
      "text": "the terrible conditions in which they were working."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92444.0,
      "end_time": 95525.0,
      "text": "More than 700 of these boats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95525.0,
      "end_time": 97832.0,
      "text": "which are fishermen boats repurposed"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97832.0,
      "end_time": 100292.0,
      "text": "with oil absorbent in white"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100293.0,
      "end_time": 102688.0,
      "text": "and oil containment in orange, were used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102688.0,
      "end_time": 105947.0,
      "text": "but they only collected three percent of the oil on the surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105947.0,
      "end_time": 107659.0,
      "text": "and the health of the cleaners"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107659.0,
      "end_time": 109572.0,
      "text": "were very deeply affected."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109572.0,
      "end_time": 113566.0,
      "text": "I was working on a very interesting technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113566.0,
      "end_time": 115875.0,
      "text": "at MIT, but it was a very long-term view"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115875.0,
      "end_time": 117309.0,
      "text": "of how to develop technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117309.0,
      "end_time": 119827.0,
      "text": "and it was going to be a very expensive technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119827.0,
      "end_time": 122274.0,
      "text": "and also it would be patented."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122275.0,
      "end_time": 124907.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to develop something that we could"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124907.0,
      "end_time": 128306.0,
      "text": "develop very fast, that would be cheap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128306.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130746.00000000001,
      "text": "and that would be open-source, so, because"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130747.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132915.0,
      "text": "oil spills are not only happening in the Gulf of Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 132915.0,
      "end_time": 135531.0,
      "text": "and that would be using renewable energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 135531.0,
      "end_time": 137931.0,
      "text": "So I quit my dream job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 137931.0,
      "end_time": 139547.0,
      "text": "and I moved to New Orleans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139547.0,
      "end_time": 142491.0,
      "text": "and I kept on studying how the oil spill was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142491.0,
      "end_time": 144563.0,
      "text": "Currently, what they were doing is"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144563.0,
      "end_time": 146208.0,
      "text": "that they were using these small fishing boats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146209.0,
      "end_time": 149369.0,
      "text": "and they were cleaning clean lines in an ocean of dirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 149369.0,
      "end_time": 153820.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re using the exact same amount of surface"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 153820.0,
      "end_time": 155234.0,
      "text": "of oil absorbent, but you&#39;re just paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 155235.0,
      "end_time": 157568.0,
      "text": "to natural patterns, and if you&#39;re going up the winds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 157568.0,
      "end_time": 159336.0,
      "text": "you can collect a lot more material."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159336.0,
      "end_time": 161457.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re multiplying the rig,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 161457.0,
      "end_time": 164310.0,
      "text": "so you multiply how many layers of absorbent"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 164320.0,
      "end_time": 165934.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re using, you can collect a lot more."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165934.0,
      "end_time": 168535.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s extremely difficult to move oil absorbent"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 168535.0,
      "end_time": 172167.0,
      "text": "against the winds, the surface currents and the waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 172167.0,
      "end_time": 173631.0,
      "text": "These are enormous forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 173631.0,
      "end_time": 176654.0,
      "text": "So the very simple idea was to use the ancient technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176654.0,
      "end_time": 178906.0,
      "text": "of sailing and tacking of the wind"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178907.0,
      "end_time": 181525.0,
      "text": "to capture or intercept the oil"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181525.0,
      "end_time": 182867.0,
      "text": "that is drifting down the wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 182867.0,
      "end_time": 186363.0,
      "text": "So this didn&#39;t require any invention."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 186364.0,
      "end_time": 188670.0,
      "text": "We just took a simple sailing boat"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 188670.0,
      "end_time": 189964.0,
      "text": "and we tried to pull something long and heavy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189964.0,
      "end_time": 192276.0,
      "text": "but as we tacked back and forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192276.0,
      "end_time": 193947.0,
      "text": "what we lost was two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193947.0,
      "end_time": 197324.0,
      "text": "we were losing pulling power and direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197324.0,
      "end_time": 201156.0,
      "text": "And so, I thought, what about if we just take the rudder"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 201156.0,
      "end_time": 202668.0,
      "text": "from the back of the boat to the front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 202668.0,
      "end_time": 204411.0,
      "text": "would we have better control?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204411.0,
      "end_time": 206627.0,
      "text": "So I built this small sailing robot"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 206627.0,
      "end_time": 207875.0,
      "text": "with the rudder at the front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207875.0,
      "end_time": 210340.0,
      "text": "and I was trying to pull something very long and heavy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210340.0,
      "end_time": 213547.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s a four-meter-long object just to pull,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213547.0,
      "end_time": 216459.0,
      "text": "and I was surprised with just a 14-centimeter rudder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216459.0,
      "end_time": 218811.0,
      "text": "I could control four meters of absorbent."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 218811.0,
      "end_time": 222627.0,
      "text": "Then I was so happy that I kept playing with the robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 222627.0,
      "end_time": 225910.0,
      "text": "and so you see the robot has"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 225910.0,
      "end_time": 226763.0,
      "text": "a front rudder here."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 226763.0,
      "end_time": 227979.0,
      "text": "Normally it&#39;s at the back."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227979.0,
      "end_time": 231594.0,
      "text": "And, playing, I realized that the maneuverability"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 231594.0,
      "end_time": 232874.0,
      "text": "of this was really amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 232874.0,
      "end_time": 234802.0,
      "text": "and I could avoid an obstacle at the very last second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 234802.0,
      "end_time": 236474.0,
      "text": "more maneuverable than a normal boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236474.0,
      "end_time": 239338.0,
      "text": "Then I started publishing online, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 239338.0,
      "end_time": 242250.0,
      "text": "some friends from Korea, they started being"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 242250.0,
      "end_time": 243979.0,
      "text": "interested in this, and we made a boat"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 243979.0,
      "end_time": 245787.0,
      "text": "which has a front rudder and a back rudder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245787.0,
      "end_time": 247845.0,
      "text": "so we started interacting with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247845.0,
      "end_time": 249964.0,
      "text": "and it was slightly better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249964.0,
      "end_time": 251888.0,
      "text": "although it was very small and a bit off balance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 251888.0,
      "end_time": 252968.0,
      "text": "but then we thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 252968.0,
      "end_time": 254856.0,
      "text": "what if we have more than two points of control?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 254856.0,
      "end_time": 256848.0,
      "text": "What if the entire boat becomes a point of control?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 256848.0,
      "end_time": 258968.0,
      "text": "What if the entire boat changes shape?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 258968.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261408.00000000003,
      "text": "So — (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 261408.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263304.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 263304.0,
      "end_time": 265888.0,
      "text": "And so that&#39;s the beginning of Protei,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 265889.0,
      "end_time": 267528.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the first boat in history"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 267528.0,
      "end_time": 269152.0,
      "text": "that completely changed the shape of the hull"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 269152.0,
      "end_time": 270322.0,
      "text": "in order to control it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 270322.0,
      "end_time": 273208.0,
      "text": "and the properties of sailing that we get"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273208.0,
      "end_time": 276106.0,
      "text": "are very superior compared to a normal boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 276106.0,
      "end_time": 278760.0,
      "text": "When we&#39;re turning, we have the feeling of surfing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 278760.0,
      "end_time": 282876.0,
      "text": "and the way it&#39;s going up-wind, it&#39;s very efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 282876.0,
      "end_time": 285575.0,
      "text": "This is low speed, low wind speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 285576.0,
      "end_time": 287649.0,
      "text": "and the maneuverability is very increased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 287649.0,
      "end_time": 289960.0,
      "text": "and here I&#39;m going to do a small jibe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 289960.0,
      "end_time": 292560.0,
      "text": "and look at the position of the sail."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292560.0,
      "end_time": 295656.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s happening is that, because the boat changes shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295656.0,
      "end_time": 297996.0,
      "text": "the position of the front sail and the main sail"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 297996.0,
      "end_time": 299173.0,
      "text": "are different to the wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 299173.0,
      "end_time": 301560.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re catching wind from both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301560.0,
      "end_time": 303315.0,
      "text": "And this is exactly what we&#39;re looking [for]"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 303315.0,
      "end_time": 305990.0,
      "text": "if we want to pull something long and heavy."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 305990.0,
      "end_time": 307488.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want to lose pulling power, nor direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 307488.0,
      "end_time": 310328.0,
      "text": "So, I wanted to know if this was possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 310328.0,
      "end_time": 311799.0,
      "text": "to put this at an industrial level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 311799.0,
      "end_time": 314311.0,
      "text": "so we made a large boat with a large sail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 314311.0,
      "end_time": 317700.0,
      "text": "and with a very light hull, inflatable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 317700.0,
      "end_time": 318512.0,
      "text": "very small footprint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 318512.0,
      "end_time": 321336.0,
      "text": "so we have a very big size and power ratio."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 321336.0,
      "end_time": 324567.0,
      "text": "After this, we wanted to see if we could"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 324567.0,
      "end_time": 326864.0,
      "text": "implement this and automate the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 326864.0,
      "end_time": 328536.0,
      "text": "so we used the same system but we added"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 328536.0,
      "end_time": 330906.0,
      "text": "a structure to it so we could activate the machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 330906.0,
      "end_time": 334120.0,
      "text": "So, we used the same bladder-inflated system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 334120.0,
      "end_time": 336104.0,
      "text": "and we took it for testing."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 336104.0,
      "end_time": 338414.0,
      "text": "So this is happening in the Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 338415.0,
      "end_time": 340946.0,
      "text": "We tried in the water without any skin or ballast"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 340946.0,
      "end_time": 343517.0,
      "text": "just to see how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 343517.0,
      "end_time": 346202.0,
      "text": "And then we mounted a camera for controlling it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 346202.0,
      "end_time": 349104.0,
      "text": "but quickly we saw that we would need"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 349104.0,
      "end_time": 351253.0,
      "text": "a lot more weight at the bottom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 351253.0,
      "end_time": 352789.0,
      "text": "so we had to take it back to the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 352790.0,
      "end_time": 354878.0,
      "text": "and then we built a skin around it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 354878.0,
      "end_time": 358164.0,
      "text": "we put batteries, remote controllers, and then"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 358165.0,
      "end_time": 359613.0,
      "text": "we put it in the water and then we"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 359613.0,
      "end_time": 362774.0,
      "text": "let it go in the water and see how well it would work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 362774.0,
      "end_time": 366198.0,
      "text": "so let some rope out, and hope it&#39;s going to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 366198.0,
      "end_time": 369421.0,
      "text": "and it worked okay, but we still have a long way."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 369421.0,
      "end_time": 371857.0,
      "text": "Our small prototype has given us good insight"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 371857.0,
      "end_time": 373203.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s working very well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 373203.0,
      "end_time": 375888.0,
      "text": "but we still need to work a lot more on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 375888.0,
      "end_time": 379757.0,
      "text": "So what we are doing is an accelerated evolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 379757.0,
      "end_time": 381205.0,
      "text": "of sailing technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 381205.0,
      "end_time": 383132.0,
      "text": "We went from a back rudder to a front rudder"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 383132.0,
      "end_time": 385143.0,
      "text": "to two rudders to multiple rudders"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 385143.0,
      "end_time": 386813.0,
      "text": "to the whole boat changing shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 386814.0,
      "end_time": 388670.0,
      "text": "and the more we are moving forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 388670.0,
      "end_time": 394717.0,
      "text": "and the more the design looks simple and cute. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 394717.0,
      "end_time": 397940.0,
      "text": "But I wanted to show you a fish because --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 397940.0,
      "end_time": 400164.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s very different from a fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 400164.0,
      "end_time": 404563.0,
      "text": "A fish will move because -- by changing like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 404564.0,
      "end_time": 407663.0,
      "text": "but our boat is propelled by the wind still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 407663.0,
      "end_time": 410700.0,
      "text": "and the hull controls the trajectory."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 410700.0,
      "end_time": 413724.0,
      "text": "So I brought to you for the first time on the TED stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 413724.0,
      "end_time": 416109.0,
      "text": "Protei Number Eight. It&#39;s not the last one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 416109.0,
      "end_time": 418358.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a good one for making demos."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 418358.0,
      "end_time": 420634.0,
      "text": "So the first thing as I show you in the video is"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 420634.0,
      "end_time": 424621.0,
      "text": "that we may be able to control the trajectory"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 424621.0,
      "end_time": 426850.0,
      "text": "of a sailing boat better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 426850.0,
      "end_time": 429145.0,
      "text": "or we may be able to never be in irons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 429146.0,
      "end_time": 430446.0,
      "text": "so never facing the wind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 430446.0,
      "end_time": 432561.0,
      "text": "we always can catch the wind from both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 432561.0,
      "end_time": 435121.0,
      "text": "But new properties of a sailing boat."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 435121.0,
      "end_time": 439376.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re looking at the boat from this side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 439377.0,
      "end_time": 441585.0,
      "text": "this might remind you of an airplane profile."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 441585.0,
      "end_time": 443998.0,
      "text": "An airplane, when you&#39;re moving in this direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 443998.0,
      "end_time": 446263.0,
      "text": "starts to lift, and that&#39;s how it takes off."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 446263.0,
      "end_time": 448438.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re taking the same system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 448438.0,
      "end_time": 450806.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re putting vertical, you&#39;re bending,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 450806.0,
      "end_time": 452806.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re moving this way forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 452806.0,
      "end_time": 455933.0,
      "text": "your instinct will tell you that you might go this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 455933.0,
      "end_time": 457740.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;re moving fast enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 457740.0,
      "end_time": 459759.0,
      "text": "you might create what we call lateral lift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 459759.0,
      "end_time": 462684.0,
      "text": "so we could get further or closer to the wind."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 462684.0,
      "end_time": 465628.0,
      "text": "Other property is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 465628.0,
      "end_time": 468789.0,
      "text": "A normal sailing boat has a centerboard here"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 468789.0,
      "end_time": 470781.0,
      "text": "and a rudder at the back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 470781.0,
      "end_time": 473331.0,
      "text": "and these two things are what creates most"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 473331.0,
      "end_time": 475985.0,
      "text": "resistance and turbulence behind the boat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 475985.0,
      "end_time": 478256.0,
      "text": "but because this doesn&#39;t have either"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 478256.0,
      "end_time": 479792.0,
      "text": "a centerboard or a rudder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 479792.0,
      "end_time": 482664.0,
      "text": "we hope that if we keep working on this hull design"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 482664.0,
      "end_time": 484856.0,
      "text": "we can improve and have less resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 484856.0,
      "end_time": 487510.0,
      "text": "The other thing is, most boats, when they reach"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 487511.0,
      "end_time": 489735.0,
      "text": "a certain speed, and they are going on waves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 489735.0,
      "end_time": 492174.0,
      "text": "they start to hit and slap on the surface of the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 492174.0,
      "end_time": 495471.0,
      "text": "and a lot of the energy moving forward is lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 495471.0,
      "end_time": 497559.0,
      "text": "But if we&#39;re going with the flow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 497559.0,
      "end_time": 499695.0,
      "text": "if we pay attention to natural patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 499695.0,
      "end_time": 501306.0,
      "text": "instead of trying to be strong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 501306.0,
      "end_time": 503705.0,
      "text": "but if you&#39;re going with the flow, we may absorb"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 503705.0,
      "end_time": 506902.0,
      "text": "a lot of environmental noises, so the wave energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 506902.0,
      "end_time": 510580.0,
      "text": "to actually save some energy to move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 510590.0,
      "end_time": 514210.0,
      "text": "So we may have developed the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 514210.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516877.00000000006,
      "text": "which is very efficient for pulling something long and heavy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 516876.0,
      "end_time": 521930.0,
      "text": "but the idea is, what is the purpose of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 521940.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523400.00000000006,
      "text": "if it doesn&#39;t reach the right hands?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 523390.0,
      "end_time": 525986.0,
      "text": "Normal technology or innovation happens like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 525986.0,
      "end_time": 528415.0,
      "text": "Somebody has an interesting idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 528416.0,
      "end_time": 530378.0,
      "text": "some other scientist or engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 530378.0,
      "end_time": 532882.0,
      "text": "they take it to the next level, they make a theory about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 532882.0,
      "end_time": 534137.0,
      "text": "and maybe they patent it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 534138.0,
      "end_time": 536674.0,
      "text": "and then some industry will make a contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 536674.0,
      "end_time": 539818.0,
      "text": "of exclusivity to manufacture and sell it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 539818.0,
      "end_time": 541914.0,
      "text": "and then, eventually, a buyer will buy it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 541914.0,
      "end_time": 544682.0,
      "text": "and we hope that they are going to use [it] for a good purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 544682.0,
      "end_time": 548378.0,
      "text": "What we really want is that this innovation happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 548378.0,
      "end_time": 550714.0,
      "text": "continuously. The inventor and engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 550714.0,
      "end_time": 552450.0,
      "text": "and also the manufacturers and everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 552450.0,
      "end_time": 554834.0,
      "text": "works at the same time, but this would be sterile"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 554834.0,
      "end_time": 558465.0,
      "text": "if this was happening in a parallel and uncrossed process."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 558466.0,
      "end_time": 560506.0,
      "text": "What you really want is not a sequential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 560506.0,
      "end_time": 561898.0,
      "text": "not parallel development."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 561898.0,
      "end_time": 563507.0,
      "text": "You want to have a network of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 563507.0,
      "end_time": 565585.0,
      "text": "You want everybody, like we&#39;re doing now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 565586.0,
      "end_time": 568755.0,
      "text": "to work at the same time, and that can only happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 568755.0,
      "end_time": 572146.0,
      "text": "if these people all together decide to share the information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 572146.0,
      "end_time": 575860.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s exactly what open hardware is about."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 575860.0,
      "end_time": 578755.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s to replace competition by collaboration."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 578755.0,
      "end_time": 582906.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s to transform any new product into a new market."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 582906.0,
      "end_time": 585347.0,
      "text": "So what is open hardware?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 585347.0,
      "end_time": 587130.0,
      "text": "Essentially, open hardware is a license."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 587130.0,
      "end_time": 589202.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just an intellectual property setup."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 589202.0,
      "end_time": 592226.0,
      "text": "It means that everybody is free to use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 592226.0,
      "end_time": 595379.0,
      "text": "modify and distribute, and in exchange"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 595379.0,
      "end_time": 596657.0,
      "text": "we only ask for two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 596657.0,
      "end_time": 598752.0,
      "text": "The name is credited -- the name of the project --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 598752.0,
      "end_time": 601488.0,
      "text": "and also the people who make improvement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 601488.0,
      "end_time": 602816.0,
      "text": "they share back with the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 602816.0,
      "end_time": 604152.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a very simple condition."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 604152.0,
      "end_time": 608176.0,
      "text": "And I started this project alone in a garage in New Orleans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 608176.0,
      "end_time": 610352.0,
      "text": "but quickly after I wanted to publish and share"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 610352.0,
      "end_time": 612960.0,
      "text": "this information, so I made a Kickstarter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 612960.0,
      "end_time": 614336.0,
      "text": "which is a crowd-fundraising platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 614336.0,
      "end_time": 616768.0,
      "text": "and in about one month we fundraised 30,000 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 616768.0,
      "end_time": 620800.0,
      "text": "With this money, I hired a team of young engineers"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 620800.0,
      "end_time": 622608.0,
      "text": "from all over the world, and we rented a factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 622608.0,
      "end_time": 624127.0,
      "text": "in Rotterdam in the Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 624128.0,
      "end_time": 627289.0,
      "text": "We were peer-learning, we were engineering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 627289.0,
      "end_time": 630472.0,
      "text": "we were making things, prototyping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 630472.0,
      "end_time": 632697.0,
      "text": "but most importantly we were trying our prototypes"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 632697.0,
      "end_time": 634392.0,
      "text": "in the water as often as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 634392.0,
      "end_time": 637544.0,
      "text": "to fail as quickly as possible, to learn from."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 637544.0,
      "end_time": 640550.0,
      "text": "This is a proud member of Protei from Korea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 640560.0,
      "end_time": 642516.0,
      "text": "and on the right side, this is a multiple-masts"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 642516.0,
      "end_time": 644449.0,
      "text": "design proposed by a team in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 644449.0,
      "end_time": 647633.0,
      "text": "This idea really appealed to Gabriella Levine"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 647634.0,
      "end_time": 650229.0,
      "text": "in New York, and so she decided to prototype"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 650229.0,
      "end_time": 652759.0,
      "text": "this idea that she saw, and she documented"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 652759.0,
      "end_time": 654188.0,
      "text": "every step of the process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 654188.0,
      "end_time": 656437.0,
      "text": "and she published it on Instructables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 656437.0,
      "end_time": 658669.0,
      "text": "which is a website for sharing inventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 658669.0,
      "end_time": 660564.0,
      "text": "Less than one week after,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 660564.0,
      "end_time": 664574.0,
      "text": "this is a team in Eindhoven, it&#39;s a school of engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 664574.0,
      "end_time": 666904.0,
      "text": "They made it, but they eventually published"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 666904.0,
      "end_time": 668280.0,
      "text": "a simplified design."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 668280.0,
      "end_time": 669957.0,
      "text": "They also made it into an Instructable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 669957.0,
      "end_time": 671692.0,
      "text": "and in less than one week, they had"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 671692.0,
      "end_time": 674452.0,
      "text": "almost 10,000 views, and they got many new friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 674452.0,
      "end_time": 677356.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re working on also simpler technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 677356.0,
      "end_time": 679307.0,
      "text": "not that complex, with younger people"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 679307.0,
      "end_time": 680876.0,
      "text": "and also older people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 680876.0,
      "end_time": 684260.0,
      "text": "like this dinosaur is from Mexico. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 684270.0,
      "end_time": 686844.0,
      "text": "So Protei is now an international network"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 686844.0,
      "end_time": 689692.0,
      "text": "of innovation for selling technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 689692.0,
      "end_time": 691484.0,
      "text": "using this shape-shifting hull."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 691484.0,
      "end_time": 695519.0,
      "text": "And what puts us together is that we have a common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 695519.0,
      "end_time": 698308.0,
      "text": "at least, global understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 698308.0,
      "end_time": 701380.0,
      "text": "of what the word \"business\" is, or what it should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 701380.0,
      "end_time": 703613.0,
      "text": "This is how most work today."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 703613.0,
      "end_time": 705987.0,
      "text": "Business as usual is saying, what&#39;s most important"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 705987.0,
      "end_time": 708226.0,
      "text": "is to make lots of profit, and you&#39;ll be using"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 708226.0,
      "end_time": 711510.0,
      "text": "technology for that, and people will be your work force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 711510.0,
      "end_time": 712299.0,
      "text": "instrumentalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 712299.0,
      "end_time": 714971.0,
      "text": "and environment is usually the last priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 714971.0,
      "end_time": 718849.0,
      "text": "It will be just a way to, say, greenwash your audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 718849.0,
      "end_time": 721800.0,
      "text": "and, say, increase your price tag."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 721800.0,
      "end_time": 723609.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re trying to do, or what we believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 723609.0,
      "end_time": 726250.0,
      "text": "because this is how we believe the world really works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 726250.0,
      "end_time": 728194.0,
      "text": "is that without the environment you have nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 728195.0,
      "end_time": 731800.0,
      "text": "We have the people so we need to protect each other, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 731800.0,
      "end_time": 732744.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re a technology company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 732744.0,
      "end_time": 737929.0,
      "text": "and profit is necessary to make this happen. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 737929.0,
      "end_time": 741534.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 741534.0,
      "end_time": 745615.0,
      "text": "If we have the courage to understand or accept"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 745615.0,
      "end_time": 747535.0,
      "text": "that this actually how the world really works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 747535.0,
      "end_time": 750552.0,
      "text": "and this is the order of priority that we need to choose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 750552.0,
      "end_time": 752693.0,
      "text": "then it makes obvious why we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 752693.0,
      "end_time": 755320.0,
      "text": "to choose open hardware for developing environmental"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 755320.0,
      "end_time": 756912.0,
      "text": "technology, because we need to share information."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 756912.0,
      "end_time": 758992.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s next for us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 758992.0,
      "end_time": 761526.0,
      "text": "So, this small machine that you&#39;ve seen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 761527.0,
      "end_time": 763671.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re hoping to make small toys like"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 763671.0,
      "end_time": 767164.0,
      "text": "one-meter remote control Protei that you can upgrade --"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 767164.0,
      "end_time": 770150.0,
      "text": "so replace the remote control parts by Androids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 770150.0,
      "end_time": 773929.0,
      "text": "so the mobile phone, and Arduino micro-controller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 773929.0,
      "end_time": 775151.0,
      "text": "so you could be controlling this"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 775152.0,
      "end_time": 776640.0,
      "text": "from your mobile phone, your tablet."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 776640.0,
      "end_time": 780206.0,
      "text": "Then what we want to do is create six-meter versions"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 780206.0,
      "end_time": 782534.0,
      "text": "so we can test the maximum performance of these machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 782534.0,
      "end_time": 784980.0,
      "text": "so we can go at very, very high speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 784980.0,
      "end_time": 785361.0,
      "text": "So imagine yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 785361.0,
      "end_time": 788545.0,
      "text": "You are laying down in a flexible torpedo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 788546.0,
      "end_time": 790400.0,
      "text": "sailing at high speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 790400.0,
      "end_time": 791885.0,
      "text": "controlling the shape of the hull with your legs"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 791885.0,
      "end_time": 794547.0,
      "text": "and controlling the sail with your arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 794547.0,
      "end_time": 798872.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s what we&#39;re looking for developing. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 798872.0,
      "end_time": 801860.0,
      "text": "And we replace the human being --"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 801860.0,
      "end_time": 803230.0,
      "text": "to go, for example, for measuring radioactivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 803230.0,
      "end_time": 805409.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t want a human to be sailing those robots --"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 805409.0,
      "end_time": 808744.0,
      "text": "with batteries, motors, micro-controllers and sensors."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 808744.0,
      "end_time": 812678.0,
      "text": "This is what our teammates, we dream of at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 812678.0,
      "end_time": 815330.0,
      "text": "We hope that we can sometime clean up oil spills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 815330.0,
      "end_time": 819307.0,
      "text": "or we can gather or collect plastic in the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 819307.0,
      "end_time": 822741.0,
      "text": "or we can have swarms of our machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 822741.0,
      "end_time": 825923.0,
      "text": "controlled by multi-player video game engines"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 825923.0,
      "end_time": 827874.0,
      "text": "to control many of these machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 827874.0,
      "end_time": 829625.0,
      "text": "to monitor coral reefs"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 829625.0,
      "end_time": 831764.0,
      "text": "or to monitor fisheries."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 831764.0,
      "end_time": 836254.0,
      "text": "Our hope is that we can use open hardware technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 836254.0,
      "end_time": 839785.0,
      "text": "to better understand and protect our oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 839785.0,
      "end_time": 843497.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 843497.0,
      "end_time": 862759.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}